application which will enable a user to use all of the available functional options of the
"Current Weather Data API"

Response for the Weather API needs to be with JSON element.

OpenWeatherMap API:
Website: https://openweathermap.org/api
after login you get the API Key APPID=1f996ae109bde37ce5565fda4eb07438"

BASE_URL = "https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather/"
query parameters: ?q={city name},{country code}

By city name
Description:
You can call by city name or city name and country code. API responds with a list of results
that match a searching word.